        self.label_48.setText(_translate("topicLessonMainWindow", "<html><head/><body><p align=\"justify\">A <span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#ff0000;\">hyperbola</span> is the set of all points ( <span style=\" font-style:italic; color:#00da00;\">x </span>, <span style=\" font-style:italic; color:#0000ff;\">y </span>) in a plane, the difference of whgose distances from two fixed points, </p><p align=\"justify\">called foci is a constant.<br/></p><p align=\"justify\">The graph of a hyperbola has two disconnected parts called <span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#ff0000;\">branches</span>. The midpoint of the line segment between the </p><p align=\"justify\">foci is the <span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#ff0000;\">center</span>. The center has distance <span style=\" font-style:italic;\">c</span> units from each of the two foci. The intersection of the hyperbola and </p><p align=\"justify\">the line joining the foci are the <span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#ff0000;\">vertices</span>. The line segments containing the vertices is called the <span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#ff0000;\">transverse axis</span> and </p><p align=\"justify\">its length is 2<span style=\" font-style:italic;\">a</span>, The line segment of legth 2<span style=\" font-style:italic;\">b</span> passing through the center and perpendicular to the transverse axis is the </p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#ff0000;\">conjugate axis</span>.</p></body></html>"))
        self.label_53.setText(_translate("topicLessonMainWindow", "<html><head/><body><p><span style=\" font-size:20pt;\">Standard Equation of Hyperbola</span></p><p>The standard equation of an ellipse with center at ( <span style=\" font-style:italic; color:#00da00;\">h </span>, <span style=\" font-style:italic; color:#0000ff;\">k </span>): </p><p>1. <span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\">( </span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline;\">x</span><span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\"> - </span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#00da00;\">h </span><span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\">)</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align:super;\">2</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; vertical-align:super;\"/><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">- </span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline;\">( y</span><span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\"> - </span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#0000ff;\">k </span><span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\">)</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align:super;\">2</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">= </span>1, when the transverse axis is horizontal.</p><p><span style=\" font-size:18pt; color:#ffffff;\">qqqq</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">a</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; vertical-align:super;\">2</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; color:#ffffff; vertical-align:super;\">qqqqqqqq</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">b</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; vertical-align:super;\">2</span></p><p>2. <span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\">( </span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline;\">y</span><span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\"> - </span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#0000ff;\">k</span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#00da00;\"/><span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\">)</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align:super;\">2</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; vertical-align:super;\"/><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">- </span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline;\">( x</span><span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\"> - </span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#00da00;\">h</span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline; color:#0000ff;\"/><span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\">)</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align:super;\">2</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">= </span>1, when the transverse axis is vertical. </p><p><span style=\" font-size:18pt; color:#ffffff;\">qqqq</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">a</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; vertical-align:super;\">2</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; color:#ffffff; vertical-align:super;\">qqqqqqqq</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">b</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; vertical-align:super;\">2</span></p><p>The vertices are <span style=\" font-style:italic;\">a</span> units from the center.</p><p>The <span style=\" font-style:italic;\">foci</span> are, <span style=\" font-style:italic;\">c</span> units from the <span style=\" font-style:italic;\">center</span> where <span style=\" font-style:italic;\">c</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic; vertical-align:super;\">2</span>= <span style=\" font-style:italic;\">a</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic; vertical-align:super;\">2</span> + <span style=\" font-style:italic;\">b</span><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic; vertical-align:super;\">2</span>.</p></body></html>"))
